l,"title":"Biologic Collagen Peptide™ Cream (J001)","subTitle":"","stockLimit":24607,"infoBanner":null,"keyBenefits":null,"size":"50ml ","description":null,"brandName":"Youthbomb™","slug":"youthbomb-biologic-collagen-peptide-cream","topUpSKU":null,"recommendedFor":"","cListRecommended":null,"candleSafety":null,"highlights":"\u003cp\u003e‎With C18™ COMPLEX: 18+% active and supercharged ingredients, featuring: \n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e ER PEPTIDES - An advanced Peptide Amino Acid Complex tailor-made to help visibly lift, firm, reduce the appearance of expression lines, and contribute to beautifully smooth-looking skin.\n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e FLOWER FERMENT FILTRATE - Helps the skin maintain moisture content and barrier function.\n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e UME FRUIT EXTRACT - Helps to improve the appearance of skin damage caused by glycation (sugar molecules binding with skin proteins).\n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e NIACINAMIDE - A multifunctional master molecule to help support the skin’s barrier, elasticity and reduce the appearance of age and sun damage spots.   \n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e MULTI-PHYTROGENS - A multi-plant complex containing phytoestrogens from extracts of Pueraria Lobata Root, Clover Flower, Cimicifuga Racemosa Root, Angelica Polymorpha Sinensis Root, Pueraria Mirifica Root, Polygonum Cuspidatum Root and Soy.\n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e SYNURUS PALMATOPINNATIFIDUS LEAF/STEM EXTRACT+ - An exclusive Japanese Grass Extract with powerful skin-soothing and redness-reducing properties.\u003cbr /\u003e\n‎\n‎\u003cstrong\u003e+\u003c/strong\u003e POTENTILLA MIYABEI CALLUS EXTRACT - Helps to improve skin barrier function and reduce transepidermal water loss (TEWL).\u003c/p\u003e","insiderProduct":"","pdpUrl":null,"product":null,"visuals":[],"media":[{"__typename":"VisualBynderType","id":"79E3E1AC-D092-4981-899BB26DA12C7F0C","description":"","name":"youthbo